Route: /users/:username
- Passes the following data to the view:

name:			Full name of the requested user.
userName:		User name of the requested user.
numberOfPosts:		The number of posts the requested user  has made.
numberOfFollowers:	Number of followers the requested user has.
profilePic: 		URL to the profile pic of the requested user
profilePic:			the navbar color for the currently logged in user
isCurrentUser: 		Whether the profile being requested is of the currently logged in User.
currentUsername: 	The user name of the currently logged in user
